hat API on the test classpath; no Docker service or environment setup is indicated.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"javax.servlet:servlet-api:2.3\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The `jackrabbit-webdav:2.0-beta4` POM declares the servlet API as a provided dependency, and the artifact contains public WebDAV servlet/request/response classes that import `javax.servlet` types.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No environment variables, system properties, or live WebDAV/Jackrabbit server are required. Prefer in-process unit tests for XML, headers, methods, reports, locators, and servlet-adapter behavior using simple stubs or mocks rather than relying on an external server.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported native-image failures in locator tests look more like version-specific behavior changes than missing setup, so Gradle and Native Image verification should remain the final authority.\",\n    \"If generated tests avoid servlet-facing classes entirely, the extra servlet API dependency may not be exercised, but it is needed for meaningful coverage of the library's normal server-side API surface.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_028fc0c48e7eb928016a42c087a6d48195b7f68e08cb7d27f1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 965, "output": 827, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22784, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782759545597, "responseId": "resp_028fc0c48e7eb928016a42c07a29508195bf7f22a020092c30"}}
